video_title: How To Get Over A Breakup #nessabarrett #breakupadvice #truelove
transcript:
I feel like you just gotta fake it until
you make it and just force yourself and
there's always going to be days I mean
like I thought there was like a day
where I was like fine and then two
seconds later I see something and I'm
bawling my eyes out you know and even
like randomly like you know months later
I'm fully moved on but I'll still get
sad over things if you ever had true
love for that person you're always going
to love them it was always hard but I
think the second that I really started
to prioritize myself rather than how
much I miss that person it helped
